2026-02-21 15:52:13 - INFO - 574 -{"payload": "{\"response\":{\"chat_message\":{\"id\":\"b4c01a78-68a4-40a8-b0b1-5ae41ffbbdf1\",\"source\":\"Travel_Planner\",\"models_usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":208,\"completion_tokens\":1069},\"metadata\":{},\"created_at\":\"2026-02-21T10:22:13.452329Z\",\"content\":\"**Two\u2011Day Mayanoor (Karur) Itinerary \u2013 INR\u202f50,000\u202fbudget**\\n\\n---\\n\\n### Day\u202f1 \u2013 Arrival & Exploration  \\n- **Morning**  \\n  - Depart from Chennai (or nearest major city) by **train** \u2013\u202f~\u202f\u20b9800\u202f(2nd\u202fclass AC) or by **private car** \u2013\u202f~\u202f\u20b92,200 (round\u2011trip, shared).  \\n  - Check\u2011in to chosen hotel (see options below).  \\n\\n- **Mid\u2011Morning**  \\n  - Breakfast at the hotel or a local dhaba \u2013\u202f\u20b9120\u2011\u20b9200.  \\n\\n- **Late Morning \u2013 Cultural Spot**  \\n  - Visit **Kalyana Pasupatheeswarar Temple** (free entry).  \\n  - Explore the **Karur Museum** \u2013\u202f\u20b930 entry.  \\n\\n- **Lunch**  \\n  - Traditional Tamil meal at **Sri Krishna Mess** \u2013\u202f\u20b9250\u202fper person.  \\n\\n- **Afternoon**  \\n  - Stroll along the **Kaveri Riverbank**, optional boat ride \u2013\u202f\u20b9150.  \\n\\n- **Evening**  \\n  - Sunset at **Mettur Dam viewpoint** (30\u202fkm drive, fuel cost ~\u20b9300).  \\n  - Dinner at **Hotel Sree Krishna** \u2013\u202f\u20b9350\u202fper person.  \\n\\n- **Night**  \\n  - Return to hotel, relax.\\n\\n---\\n\\n### Day\u202f2 \u2013 Nature & Local Life  \\n- **Early Breakfast** \u2013\u202f\u20b9150.  \\n\\n- **Morning**  \\n  - Day\u2011trip to **Kollidam River Eco\u2011Park** \u2013\u202f\u20b9100 entry, bike rental \u20b980.  \\n\\n- **Mid\u2011Morning Snack** \u2013\u202f\u20b9100 (fresh fruit/tea).  \\n\\n- **Lunch**  \\n  - Picnic with packed tiffin from hotel \u2013\u202f\u20b9200.  \\n\\n- **Afternoon**  \\n  - Visit **Karur Handloom Weaving Centre** \u2013\u202ffree, shop for souvenirs (budget \u20b9500\u2011\u20b91,000).  \\n\\n- **Late Afternoon**  \\n  - Coffee break at **Cafe Aroma** \u2013\u202f\u20b9150.  \\n\\n- **Evening**  \\n  - Return to hotel, freshen up.  \\n  - Dinner at **Hotel Sree Krishna** (same as Day\u202f1) \u2013\u202f\u20b9350.  \\n\\n- **Departure**  \\n  - Catch evening train or drive back (same transport cost as Day\u202f1).\\n\\n---\\n\\n### Accommodation (choose one)\\n\\n- **Budget** \u2013 *Hotel Sri Krishna* (basic rooms, clean, central) \u2013\u202f\u20b91,200\u202f/night.  \\n- **Mid\u2011range** \u2013 *Hotel Green Park* (air\u2011conditioned, breakfast included) \u2013\u202f\u20b92,200\u202f/night.  \\n- **Luxury** \u2013 *The Karur Residency* (spa, pool, premium service) \u2013\u202f\u20b94,500\u202f/night.\\n\\n*All rates are approximate and per double occupancy.*\\n\\n---\\n\\n### Approximate Cost Breakdown (per couple)\\n\\n| Item | Approx. Cost (INR) |\\n|------|-------------------|\\n| Transport (train round\u2011trip) | 1,600 |\\n| Fuel/Car (shared) | 2,200 |\\n| Hotel (2 nights) \u2013 budget | 2,400 |\\n| Hotel \u2013 mid | 4,400 |\\n| Hotel \u2013 luxury | 9,000 |\\n| Food (breakfast, lunch, dinner, snacks) | 5,500 |\\n| Activities & entry fees | 800 |\\n| Miscellaneous (souvenirs, tips) | 1,000 |\\n| **Total (budget option)** | **\u2248\u202f13,500** |\\n| **Total (mid\u2011range)** | **\u2248\u202f15,900** |\\n| **Total (luxury)** | **\u2248\u202f21,300** |\\n\\nEven with the luxury stay, the total stays well under the **\u20b950,000** ceiling, leaving ample room for extra shopping or an upgraded transport mode.\\n\\n---\\n\\n### Quick Tips\\n- Book train tickets 2\u20133 days in advance via IRCTC to secure seats.  \\n- Carry a small bottle of water and sunscreen for river\u2011bank walks.  \\n- Cash is preferred at local eateries; ATMs are limited.  \\n- Dress modestly when visiting temples (cover shoulders/knees).  \\n\\nEnjoy a relaxed, culturally rich getaway in Mayanoor!  \\n\\n**APPROVE**\",\"type\":\"TextMessage\"},\"inner_messages\":[]},\"name\":\"Travel_Planner\"}", "sender": "Travel_Planner_d1d2cd4a-e51f-433e-a062-3278ff03f83d/d1d2cd4a-e51f-433e-a062-3278ff03f83d", "receiver": null, "kind": "MessageKind.PUBLISH", "delivery_stage": "DeliveryStage.DELIVER", "type": "Message"}
